					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Nanase had some family matters to attend to, and Hotori's gotten home way ahead of us, since she's on a bike.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"奈奈濑好象有家务事，畔也骑脚踏车回去了。",
